    <system:String x:Key="Contact_Info_Text">If you need to contact me for any reason, you can reach me here:</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Terms_of_Service">Terms of Service</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Terms_of_Service_Part1">This programme is my property and I reserve the right to change the Terms of Service for future versions as I see fit.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Terms_of_Service_Part2">I am not liable for any harm that may be caused by using this programme.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Terms_of_Service_Part2_Extra">Having said that, PLEASE make backups of your personal data. I try my best, but I am not perfect, so mistakes can happen.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Terms_of_Service_Part3">This programme is free. If you paid money to get it, somebody tried to scam you. If so, try to get your money back swiftly. The only official places to get this programme are listed above, under 'Contact Info'.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Terms_of_Service_Part3_Extra">I do appreciate however any and all voluntary donations.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Legal_Notice">Third-Party Tools and Software</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Legal_Notice_Text">This programme was made using Microsoft Visual Studio 2022, .NET Framework 4, C#, and WPF. Additionally, the packages Microsoft.Bcl (1.1.10), Microsoft.Bcl.Async (1.0.168), and Microsoft.Bcl.Build (1.0.21) were used.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Special_Thanks">Special Thanks</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Special_Thanks_Text">
        I want to thank my family for supporting me.
    I also want to thank Ravensburg-Weingarten University of Applied Sciences for teaching me what I needed to know to create this programme.
    Naturally, credit is due to Maxis and Will Wright for establishing such a unique game series.
    Additional thanks go to the creators of the used third-party software as well as s3pe, s3rc, Delphy's Sims 3 Pack Multi-Extracter, and Sims3Pack File Generate Tool.
    And some very big thanks are due to the Community of The Sims 3 and The Sims in general. Without you and your constant contributions, the games would not be the same as they are today.
    </system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Special_Thanks_Text_Part2">
        And now to the most important part: Here could be YOUR name! Jokes aside, if you donate me some money, no matter how little, I will put your name in here from the next released version onward. For more information visit my Patreon page. The link is above, under 'Contact Info'.
    </system:String>

